column5: Hey everyone  Well tomorrows the day, got the guide all booked and headed out tomorrow morning.... hittin the water around 8 Am. We will be hitting a couple lakes in the Orlando area. Not sure exactly which ones, but Ill be sure to mention them in the report.  The wife and I are going together, Im hoping she catches a nice BIG one so it will give her the taste of what its like... hahah then she might be a little easier on me when I want to go out back home !  So its time for bed ( long day at Universal Studios ).... early rise tomorrow.  WISH ME LUCK !!! The report will be here tomorrow night !!! Hopefully with a picture of my fist down a fishes mouth !!!!!   Talk to you soon !
All the best to you man hope the wife lands a few
have fun , when i was there in january i wanted to go fishing but I couldn't get anyone to go with me and the wife was too busy at the shopping centres.
I know I'm kind of late but....  best of luck to you
Wemen.LOL  Looking forward to the report.
A 10 would be nice? Good Fishing!

hahah Well.... GREAT DAY !!!! no 10 pounder but I did get a 5 !!!! Its feels beautiful settin the hook on something that big. We caught about 25 fish all together with an average size being in the 2lbs range !  I dont have a way to get the pics off the camera so the ACTUALL report will be next week !!!  Talk to everyone soon !
